Hello, great mod!

I was wondering if it's possible to assign a different missile with the reloadble rail without going to SPH. I can reload the same missile, but not a different one. 

I tried using the "Reassign" button but nothing happens. Is there anything I have to do to be able to reassign different missiles?

Thank you!

On 1/13/2019 at 4:36 PM, Lima said:

Hello, great mod!

I was wondering if it's possible to assign a different missile with the reloadble rail without going to SPH. I can reload the same missile, but not a different one. 

I tried using the "Reassign" button but nothing happens. Is there anything I have to do to be able to reassign different missiles?

Thank you!

Reassign only valid if you use any method(mostly KIS) to mount a new missile on the rail. The rail will "remember" the new missile.

Edit: I even tried using the premade carrier and it still does it.
